# Token Standards Implementation Guide

## Quick Start Checklist

### Phase 1: Planning (Day 1)
1. [ ] Choose token standard based on use case
2. [ ] Design tokenomics and distribution
3. [ ] Plan security and compliance requirements
4. [ ] Set up development environment

### Phase 2: Development (Days 2-5)
1. [ ] Implement base token contract
2. [ ] Add required extensions
3. [ ] Integrate neural features (if needed)
4. [ ] Write comprehensive tests

### Phase 3: Security (Days 6-7)
1. [ ] Conduct internal security review
2. [ ] Schedule external audit
3. [ ] Fix identified issues
4. [ ] Prepare deployment scripts

### Phase 4: Deployment (Day 8)
1. [ ] Deploy to testnet
2. [ ] Verify and test on testnet
3. [ ] Deploy to mainnet
4. [ ] Initialize and verify

## Step-by-Step Implementation

### Step 1: Choose Your Template
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Gitdigital-products/Token-Standards.git
cd Token-Standards

# Choose your starting point:
# 1. ERC-20: contracts/ERC20/MyToken.sol
# 2. ERC-721: contracts/ERC721/MyNFT.sol  
# 3. ERC-1155: contracts/ERC1155/MultiToken.sol
# 4. Neural-enhanced: Check the Neural* contracts